    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150390/extras/a42ded323ba3d6f99abb1d95c2833944.avif?t=1769014252\" width=512 height=64 /></span><br>Buntasy comes packed with both single-player and multiplayer campaigns and mini-games!<br><br>All of the campaign maps were made using the in-built map/unit editor so try them out to see what super fun stuff can be made with these tools.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150390/extras/2f02b959d2e1f89a09e60e627b94bfa8.poster.avif?t=1769014252\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150390/extras/2f02b959d2e1f89a09e60e627b94bfa8.webm?t=1769014252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150390/extras/2f02b959d2e1f89a09e60e627b94bfa8.mp4?t=1769014252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150390/extras/2b3317b800b661176f8e0f669e92af58.avif?t=1769014252\" width=512 height=64 /></span><br>Create your own fun mini-games that you can play by yourself or online with friends.<br><br>You can make all kinds of games such as shooter games, ball games, puzzle games, platforming games, and so on. Or perhaps some combination of these! There are no limits with the map editor!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150390/extras/94b6d9f0477cb730b759bcb926b46dcb.poster.avif?t=1769014252\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150390/extras/94b6d9f0477cb730b759bcb926b46dcb.webm?t=1769014252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150390/extras/94b6d9f0477cb730b759bcb926b46dcb.mp4?t=1769014252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150390/extras/f973b61e6afe4e4dddea35b8f0bb7f72.avif?t=1769014252\" width=512 height=64 /></span><br>Build custom units such as cars, tanks, planes, a 3-headed T-Rex, a giant gorilla, etc. Whatever you can think of, the unit creator can make it!<br><br>These units can be placed in your mini-games and be equipped with their own AI or you can control them yourself with your player character!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150390/extras/a6ce8ce3a10a4c187a0927a4d758fd07.poster.avif?t=1769014252\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150390/extras/a6ce8ce3a10a4c187a0927a4d758fd07.webm?t=1769014252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150390/extras/a6ce8ce3a10a4c187a0927a4d758fd07.mp4?t=1769014252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150390/extras/d452f1b1110b459cfa8246d2a357dd30.avif?t=1769014252\" width=512 height=64 /></span><br>Download and enjoy all the awesome mini-games and custom units made by the player community.<br><br>You can also share your own cool creations with the other players.",
